events.title: React Native Conference 2025
events.description: Join the largest React Native conference of the year! Learn from industry experts, network with fellow developers, and discover the latest trends in mobile development. This full-day event features workshops, keynotes, and hands-on sessions.

events.title: TypeScript Workshop
events.description: Master TypeScript in this intensive hands-on workshop. Perfect for developers looking to enhance their JavaScript skills with static typing. Learn advanced patterns, best practices, and real-world applications.

events.title: Mobile UX Design Meetup
events.description: Explore the latest trends in mobile user experience design. Network with designers, developers, and product managers while discussing best practices for creating intuitive mobile interfaces.

events.title: Startup Pitch Night
events.description: Watch promising startups pitch their ideas to a panel of investors and industry experts. Network with entrepreneurs, investors, and fellow innovators in the startup ecosystem.

events.title: AI & Machine Learning Summit
events.description: Dive deep into the world of artificial intelligence and machine learning. Learn about the latest algorithms, tools, and applications from leading researchers and industry practitioners.

events.title: Open Source Community Day
events.description: Celebrate open source software with fellow developers and contributors. Participate in code sprints, learn about new projects, and discover how to contribute to the open source community.
